            <h4>How to get there</h4>
            <p>Dipolog City is in northern Mindanao. It is accessible by land, sea, and air from any point in the Philippines. It is barely an hour and fifteen minutes by plane from Manila and 30 minutes by plane from Cebu. There are daily flights from Dipolog to Manila and thrice weekly to Cebu.
                There are several trips by boat every day to Dumaguete, Cebu and Bohol. Rural Transit travels to Zamboanga City and other cities in Mindanao every hour daily.</p>
